('DELL 2020 ALL IN ONE -WIFI-BLUTOOTH All in One PC', '<div class="tabFeature inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">\r\n<div class="topImgContainer" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<div class="bottomContent inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Available with Windows 8.1</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; designed for a smooth, versatile PC experience.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">\r\n<div class="leftImgContainer" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<div class="rightContent inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Smart performance in a slimmer design</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nThe Inspiron 15 features 3rd Gen Intel&reg; Core&trade; processors in a sleek design that&rsquo;s 21 percent&nbsp;thinner than the 2011 model. So you get all the performance you need, with a little more room in your bag for the other things that matter.</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="allPurposeClear" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">\r\n<div class="leftImgContainer" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><img alt="Inspiron 15 Laptop" itemprop="image" src="http://i.dell.com/sites/imagecontent/products/PublishingImages/inspiron-15-3521/images/laptop-inspiron-15-3521-pdp-design-1.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" title="Inspiron 15 Laptop" />\r\n<div class="rightContent inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Megatasking is the new multitasking</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nOne thing at a time? No way. With powerful Intel&reg; Core&trade; processors and Windows 8 apps for social media, news and more, you can turn around tasks in a flash, no matter where you are.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Watch it your way</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nPack hours of TV shows on the Inspiron 15&rsquo;s spacious hard drive or pop a movie in the DVD-RW drive. Either way, you&rsquo;ll get lost in the 15.6&quot; HD Truelife display. At home, connect to an HDMI&trade;-capable TV or monitor for an even bigger view.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<a class="tooltip microcontent" href="http://www.dell.com/mc.ashx?id=Inline-Messaging:inspiron-15-3521-modal-1b&amp;c=us&amp;l=en&amp;s=dfh&amp;modalwidth=400&amp;modalHeight=150&amp;ovropac=0&amp;modalscroll=yes&amp;modaltarget=div&amp;modaltype=tooltip&amp;position=bottom&amp;title=Find%20Out%20More%20%E2%80%BA&amp;flip=true&amp;eventType=rollover" name="modalRoll" rel="Inline-Messaging:inspiron-15-3521-modal-1b" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-decoration: none; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: absolute; z-index: 1070; display: block; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; opacity: 0;">Find Out More &rsaquo;</a></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="allPurposeClear" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">\r\n<div class="rightImgContainer" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><img alt="Inspiron 15 Laptop" itemprop="image" src="http://i.dell.com/sites/imagecontent/products/PublishingImages/inspiron-15-3521/images/laptop-inspiron-15-3521-pdp-design-2.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" title="Inspiron 15 Laptop" />\r\n<div class="leftContent inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Slim and stylish</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nStarting at just over 1&quot; thin, Inspiron 15 slips easily into a travel bag&nbsp;when you&rsquo;re on the move. Its textured lid and palm rest help you get a grip on things.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Essential features</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nFoster your creative side or crunch the numbers. The choice is yours with a 10-key number pad, 8-in-1 media card reader, USB 3.0 ports and more.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<a class="tooltip microcontent" href="http://www.dell.com/mc.ashx?id=Inline-Messaging:inspiron-15-3521-modal-2b&amp;c=us&amp;l=en&amp;s=dfh&amp;modalwidth=400&amp;modalHeight=150&amp;ovropac=0&amp;modalscroll=yes&amp;modaltarget=div&amp;modaltype=tooltip&amp;position=bottom&amp;title=Find%20Out%20More%20%E2%80%BA&amp;flip=true&amp;eventType=rollover" name="modalRoll" rel="Inline-Messaging:inspiron-15-3521-modal-2b" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-decoration: none; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: absolute; z-index: 1070; display: block; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; opacity: 0;">Find Out More &rsaquo;</a><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Charge ahead</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nStay powered up long enough to skip the in-flight movie, polish your presentation and drift off to your favorite music. Opt for the 65WHr 6-cell battery to take it even further.</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="allPurposeClear" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">\r\n<div class="leftImgContainer" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<div class="rightContent inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Designed for the real world &mdash; because that&#39;s where life happens.</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nWe want you to love your new PC for years to come. That&#39;s why we test every Inspiron laptop for reliability not just in the places where you expect it, but for the open road ahead.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">&bull; Turn up the heat: From locker rooms to locked cars, we test Inspiron laptops for survival in harsh short-term heat conditions of up to 65&deg;C/149&deg;F.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&bull; Everything hinges on it: We test Inspiron laptop hinges to ensure they still feel tight, even after opening and closing the lid 20,000 times.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&bull; Keys to success: We test commonly used keys for 10 million keystrokes and touch pad buttons 1 million times with no failure. So go ahead, finish your novel.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&bull; Buttoned up: No matter what you set your power and multimedia buttons to do, we&#39;ve tested them all to survive up to 40,000 pushes with no problems.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&bull; Twist and turn: Call us excessive, but after twisting every Inspiron laptop&#39;s base and lid more than 25,000 times, we can assure you the parts inside are well protected.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&bull; Always a good fit: You&#39;ll probably never need to remove and reinstall your Inspiron&#39;s battery 750 times, but you can rest easy knowing that we&#39;ve tested even that.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="allPurposeClear" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">\r\n<div class="ThreeXImageTop" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin: 0px; font-size: 2em; padding: 0px 0px 0.75em;">Complete your Inspiron experience</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;">Your Inspiron laptop is just the start. Look for these great additions when finalizing your purchase.</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<div class="columnsThree" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><img alt="Inspiron 15 Laptop" itemprop="image" src="http://i.dell.com/sites/imagecontent/products/PublishingImages/inspiron-14-15-17-shared/laptop-inspiron-pdp-design-3a.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" title="Inspiron 15 Laptop" />\r\n<div class="columnText" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Software</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nYour Inspiron laptop comes preloaded with anti-virus and videoconference software to help you stay protected and connected.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columnsThree" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><img alt="Inspiron 15 Laptop" itemprop="image" src="http://i.dell.com/sites/imagecontent/products/PublishingImages/inspiron-14-15-17-shared/laptop-inspiron-pdp-design-3b.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" title="Inspiron 15 Laptop" />\r\n<div class="columnText" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Services</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\nWe&rsquo;re here and ready to help. In addition to America&rsquo;s Best Standard Support (90 days Premium Phone Support and 1 year of In-Home Service After Remote Diagnosis),<a class="technote microcontent" href="http://www.dell.com/mc.ashx?id=technotes:remote-diagnosis1&amp;c=us&amp;l=en&amp;s=dfh&amp;modalwidth=400&amp;modalHeight=150&amp;ovropac=0&amp;modalscroll=yes&amp;modaltarget=div&amp;modaltype=tooltip&amp;position=bottom&amp;title=Important%20Details&amp;flip=false&amp;eventType=rollover" name="modalPopup" rel="technotes:remote-diagnosis1" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-decoration: none; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13px !important; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: 0px; color: red;">1</span></a>&nbsp;Dell offers protection options including Accidental Damage Service,<a class="technote microcontent" href="http://www.dell.com/mc.ashx?id=technotes:accidental-damage-service-disclaimer&amp;c=us&amp;l=en&amp;s=dfh&amp;modalwidth=400&amp;modalHeight=150&amp;ovropac=0&amp;modalscroll=yes&amp;modaltarget=div&amp;modaltype=tooltip&amp;position=bottom&amp;title=Important%20Details&amp;flip=false&amp;eventType=rollover" name="modalPopup" rel="technotes:accidental-damage-service-disclaimer" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-decoration: none; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13px !important; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: 0px; color: red;">2</span></a>&nbsp;LoJack for Laptops&reg;<a class="technote microcontent" href="http://www.dell.com/mc.ashx?id=technotes:lojack&amp;c=us&amp;l=en&amp;s=dfh&amp;modalwidth=400&amp;modalHeight=150&amp;ovropac=0&amp;modalscroll=yes&amp;modaltarget=div&amp;modaltype=tooltip&amp;position=bottom&amp;title=Important%20Details&amp;flip=false&amp;eventType=rollover" name="modalPopup" rel="technotes:lojack" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-decoration: none; outline: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13px !important; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: 0px; color: red;">3</span></a>&nbsp;and McAfee&reg; SecurityCenter.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, 'en', 79),
