(' Samsung Galaxy Galaxy J1 (White color)', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.714286rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">The Samsung Galaxy J1 is a wonderful Android based smartphone that comes loaded with a bunch of useful connectivity and entertainment features. This phone comes in a cool looking ceramic white color. The device&rsquo;s highlighting feature is its 4.3inch TFT touchscreen that has a display resolution of 480 x 800 pixels. A 5MP CMOS camera embedded in its back, as well as the front facing 2MP camera, is sure to please shutterbugs of all kinds. Support for multiformat media files enables you to upload all your favorite tunes onto this mobile. The phone&rsquo;s 3G support and WiFi bring high speed Internet connectivity at your fingertips. USB 2.0 and Bluetooth 4.0 are the other connectivity options that are featured on this device. The smartphone saves all your data files on its 4GB internal storage, which can be bumped up by microSD cards of up to 128GB capacity.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<img alt="Ergonomic Design" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2015/Samsung/Galaxy-J1-4GB-4G-LTE-White/feature-1.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="marb-10" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: opensans, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 0.2rem; font-size: 1.57143rem; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; margin-bottom: 10px !important; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-wei