CTURES AND VIDEOS WITHOUT TOUCHING THE DEDICATED SHUTTER BUTTON. THE PHONE COMES WITH PALM SELFIE FEATURE THAT ENABLES YOU TO SHOOT PHOTOS BY DETECTING THE MOVEMENT OF YOUR HAND GESTURE. ANOTHER WORTHWHILE FEATURE OF THIS MOBILE IS THE TAP TO TAKE PICS THAT TAKES PHOTOS WHEN YOU TAP ANYWHERE ON THE SCREEN<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<img alt="Ultra Power Saving Mode" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2015/Samsung/Galaxy-J1-4GB-4G-LTE-White/feature-3.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="marb-10" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: opensans, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-top: 0.2rem; font-size: 1.57143rem; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; margin-bottom: 10px !important; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; line-height: inherit;">ULTRA POWER SAVING MODE</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.714286rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: opensans, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">THE SAMSUNG GALAXY J1 FEATURES THE ULTRA POWER SAVING MODE, WHICH, WHEN SWITCHED ON, SHUTS DOWN UNWANTED FUNCTIONS, THUS REDUCING BATTERY CONSUMPTION SIGNIFICANTLY. NOW YOU CAN CONTINUE RECEIVING MESSAGES AND MAKING CALLS EVEN WHEN YOUR BATTERY IS LOW<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<img alt="Bright Pictures like Never Before" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2015/Samsung/G