(853, 1, NULL, 'QOT5', 663.126, 1, 20, 0.00, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-02 13:39:04', 13, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 10, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy E5 Double SIM Card connection - 16 GB, the fourth generation, Wi-Fi (Black)', '<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; font-size: 1.42857rem; padding: 0px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; word-break: break-word; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">DESIGN AND DISPLAY</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.714286rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: opensans, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">THIS DEVICE HAS SLENDER DIMENSIONS OF 141.6 X 70.2 X 7.3MM AND IS LIGHT IN WEIGHT, MAKING IT COMFORTABLE TO HOLD AND EASY TO OPERATE. THE PHONE IS AVAILABLE IN A RICH BLACK COLOR AND IS QUITE A BEAUTY. CRAFTED WITH PERFECTION, THIS PHONE FEATURES A WIDE 5INCH DISPLAY THAT USES THE SUPER AMOLED TECHNOLOGY. THIS TECHNOLOGY PRODUCES BRIGHT AND VIBRANT COLORS THAT MAKE ALL YOUR CONTENT SEEM REALISTIC AND LIVELY. ENJOY HIGH RESOLUTION IMAGES THAT MAKE YOUR USAGE TIME ENTIRELY WORTHWHILE.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; font-size: 1.42857rem; padding: 0px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; word-break: break-word; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">HARDWARE AND OPERATING SYSTEM</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.714286rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: opensans, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">ENJOY A SMOOTH AND EFFICIENT PERFORMANCE ON THIS AMAZING SMARTPHONE, WITH THE EFFICIENT QUAD CORE PROCESSOR THAT HAS A CAPACITY OF 1.2GHZ. THIS PROCESSOR BOOSTS PERFORMANCE OF YOUR SMARTPHONE, DELIVERING RESULTS THAT YOU CAN EXPERIENCE IN THE FORM OF BLISTERING APP LOADING SPEEDS. THE ANDROID V4.4.4 KITKAT OPERATING SYSTEM IS THE REASON ALL YOUR FUNCTIONS RUN SMOOTHLY. IT COMES WITH A REFINED ICON SYSTEM AND WIDGETS THAT LET YOU CUSTOMIZE YOUR HOME AND LOCK SCREEN. YOU ALSO HAVE ACCESS TO APPS, GAMES, AND MULTIMEDIA THAT YOU CAN DOWNLOAD FROM GOOGLE PLAY STORE.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; font-size: 1.42857rem; padding: 0px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; word-break: break-word; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">MULTIMEDIA</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.714286rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: opensans, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">THE SAMSUNG GALAXY E5 FEATURES AN INCREDIBLE 8MP REAR CAMERA AND A MARVELOUS 5MP FRONT CAMERA. THESE CAMERAS CAPTURE YOUR PRIZED MOMENTS WITH CLEAR AND CRISP CLARITY THAT MAKES CHERISHED MEMORIES COME ALIVE IN THE MOST EXPRESSIVE WAY POSSIBLE. THE MAIN CAMERA LETS YOU SHOOT HIGH RESOLUTION VIDEOS AT RESOLUTIONS OF 1080P AT THE RATE OF 30 FRAMES PER SECOND. IT COMES BUILT IN WITH A NUMBER OF FUNCTIONS THAT INCLUDE THE TOUCH FOCUS, FACE DETECTION, AND PANORAMA FEATURE. ITS FRONT CAMERA TURNS OUT TO BE VERY USEFUL WHILE MAKING VIDEOS CALLS, SKYPING, AND ALSO CAPTURING SELFIES. THIS DEVICE ALSO FEATURES A MUSIC PLAYER THAT SUPPORTS DIFFERENT FILE FORMATS, SO THAT YOU CAN LISTEN TO ALL YOUR FAVORITE FEET TAPPING SONGS THROUGHOUT THE DAY. CARRY OUT ALL WORK RELATED TASKS ON THIS DEVICE, AS IT COMES WITH A DOCUMENT VIEWER THAT LETS YOU VIEW FILES OF DIFFERENT FORMATS, MAKING LIFE ON THE GO MUCH EASIER.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin: 0.2rem 0px 0.5rem; font-size: 1.42857rem; padding: 0px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; word-break: break-word; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">CONNECTIVITY</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.714286rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: opensans, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-transform: uppercase; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">THE PHONE COMES WITH A VARIETY OF FEATURES TO KEEP YOU CONNECTED TO PEOPLE THAT MATTER TO YOU. IT HAS A NUMBER OF FUNCTIONS THAT INCLUDE THE BLUETOOTH V4.0 THAT ENABLES YOU TO ESTABLISH WIRELESS CONNECTIVITY QUICKLY AND EASILY. YOU ALSO HAVE THE MICROUSB V2.0 PORT THAT ENABLES SMOOTH AND QUICK TRANSFER OF FILES. THIS PHONE COMES WITH A DUAL SIM CARD OPTION THAT LETS YOU INSERT TWO DIFFERENT SIM CARDS OF SEPARATE NETWORKS, THEREBY ENABLING YOU TO MAINTAIN TWO SEPARATE NUMBERS WITH EASE. YOU CAN BROWSE THE INTERNET AND SKIM THROUGH SOCIAL MEDIA SITES AT BLAZING SPEEDS, AS THIS DEVICE SUPPORTS 4G AND WIFI CONNECTIVITY OPTIONS.</p>\r\n', 'ar', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
