(855, 1, NULL, 'QOT7', 622.351, 1, 20, 0.00, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-02 13:51:34', 13, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 10, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'HTC Desire 816G Dual Sim - 8GB, 3G + Wifi, White', '<article style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">The HTC Desire 816 Dual Sim is a great phone for those who love to capture life&#39;s precious moments in pictures. Because a picture speaks a thousand words, the HTC Desire 816 Dual Sim gives you two incredibly awesome cameras that produce high resolution pictures and videos. It has a powerful 13MP main camera at the back and a handy 5MP camera in the front that ensures all your memories and experiences are captured in vivid detail and stunning clarity, bright colors and sharp contrast. It has a wide 5.5inch HD720 screen that gives crystal clear output.This phone is backed by the advanced Qualcomm Snapdragon 400 1.3GHz quad core processor which gives you powerful performance and the Android OS that makes that performance smooth. This excellence in performance and functionality is combined by a strong battery, so your fun lasts longer. Embedded with the Li polymer battery, your mobile remains powered longer. This battery has a capacity of 2600mAh that converts to approximately 21 hours of talk time and 736 of standby time when operating on the 3G network.</article>\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">&nbsp;</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<img alt="Advanced Camera" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2014/HTC/Desire_816_Dual_Sim/advanced_camera_white.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">ADVANCED CAMERA</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">This little entertainer was created for those who love to chronicle those special moments. If you love the camera and/or the camera loves you, then the HTC Desire 816 Dual Sim is the way to go. It has a powerful 13MP camera that enables you to click pictures and videos in high resolution. The camera consists of an Accelerometer, Proximity sensor, and Ambient light sensor. The main 13MP camera consists of a 28mm lens, a BSI sensor, and produces a resolution of 1080p when recording videos, the last two of which also hold true for the 5MP front camera. The front camera is perfect for those attractive selfies, as well as those long Skype conversations. This phone is packed with a variety of features one of which is the Zoe Highlights feature which enables you to create your own videos and then send it across to friends and family or just post it on Facebook. This is sharing made so much easier.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<img alt="5.5 inch HD Display" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2014/HTC/Desire_816_Dual_Sim/hd_display_white.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">5.5 INCH HD DISPLAY</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">Enjoy your favourite movies, the hottest YouTube videos, spend hours on online browsing and view all those photos and much more on the huge 5.5inch HD display screen. This phone is fitted with HTC BoomSound, a pair of dual front facing speakers that deliver great audio. The HTC Desire 816 Dual Sim is also equipped with the HTC BlinkFeed that gives your regular and real time info feeds into Facebook, Twitter, sports and a lot more.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<img alt="Fast with 1.3GHz Quad Core Processor" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2014/HTC/Desire_816_Dual_Sim/processor_white.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">FAST WITH 1.3GHZ QUAD CORE PROCESSOR</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">The powerful 1.3GHz quad core processor takes multitasking to a whole new level. You can now browse the web, play games, read the news, watch videos and lots more seamlessly and a lot faster. Get more immersed in your game with the rich graphic details, speedy loading times and lag free gaming whilst opening multiple apps at once. This phone, as its name suggests, supports two SIM cards and enables you to switch between data plans, whilst combining your personal and business lines.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<img alt="Brilliance of Design" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2014/HTC/Desire_816_Dual_Sim/design_white.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">BRILLIANCE OF DESIGN</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(60, 63, 68); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.6001px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">The HTC Desire 816 Dual Sim has a dynamic design that is a complete knockout. It has a slim form factor, with softer curves and thinner edges. The sleek and huge 5.5inch screen adds to the elegance of the design. This phone is available in a smart white color.</span>', 'ar', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
