(851, 1, NULL, 'QOT3', 1276.356, 1, 20, 0.00, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-02 13:26:13', 13, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 11, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 11, 0, NULL, NULL, 'iPhone 6 Space Gray 16GB', '<h3 class="marb-10" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, ''Helvetica Neue Light'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(81, 81, 81); margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 18px;">Phone 6 The Apple iPhone 6 makes a grand entry in the market armed with the latest technologies, state of the art design and a splendid performance. Other smartphones don&rsquo;t stand a chance at the side of this genius that is equipped with the iOS 8 operating system that happens to be the world&rsquo;s most advanced operating system. This operating system works in perfect symphony with the phone and makes the most of the huge 4.7inch Retina HD display. This display smoothly merges with the sleek Space Gray metal body and uses the amazing IPS technology to give you a wider viewing and brighter imagery. Enjoy HIGH RESOLUTIONS of 1334 x 750 pixels and a contrast ratio of 1400:1. The iPhone 6 uses the amazing A8 chip along with the 128 bit architecture that delivers more power to do justice to that huge display. The M8 motion coprocessor lets you stay up for longer with efficient usage of power.</span><img alt="design" class="lazy" data-="" src="http://cms.souqcdn.com/spring/images/2014/Apple/iphone_6/design.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; opacity: 0.9; margin: 0px 10px 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 9px; text-align: center; display: inline;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 18px;" />\r\n<br style="box-sizing: border-box; ma